{"tid":2146195,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美議員提「改造聯合國」議案  對抗「惡意全球行為者」","createTime":"2020-08-08T12:04:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T13:37:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7367f25910e712b8395c1b75aad8de6f17873007","tid":2146195,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院共和黨議員提出改造聯合國議案，加強美國在聯合國的領導力，並對抗「惡意全球行為者」。<br />\n<br />\n據美國之音報導，美國眾議院外交委員會首席共和黨議員、眾院中國工作組（China Task Force）主席麥考爾（Michael McCaul）週五（8月7日）推出《2020年聯合國透明與問責法案》（United Nations Transparency and Accountability Act of 2020），通過對聯合國進行關鍵的改革來增強美國在聯合國的領導力與接觸。<br />\n<br />\n對抗惡毒影響<br />\n<br />\n報導稱，議案要求美國國務卿對決心在聯合國系統內部從事違背《聯合國憲章》的惡意影響力行為的成員國提出報告，並授權美國總統將這些成員國列為「惡意全球行為者」，以對抗聯合國系統內部的惡意影響活動。<br />\n<br />\n提高美國領導力<br />\n<br />\n議案授權將目前聯合國的美國公民單位（American Citizens Unit）擴充為美國公民辦公室，促進所有國際組織僱用美國公民，對支持美國公民出任國際組織領導人的努力進行協調，並要求美國國務卿將美國資助的青年專業人員（Junior Professional Officer）的職位增加50%；<br />\n<br />\n會費透明與問責<br />\n<br />\n議案要求擴大目前有關美國向聯合國交納會費的報告程序，要求報告在向國會提交後的14天內在網上公布，使公眾能夠看到。<br />\n<br />\n美國之音報導稱，麥考爾議員對此指出，中共和其他惡意行為者為了達到自己的目的，多年來對聯合國系統進行滲透。該法案將啟動關鍵改革，提高透明度，確保美國政府擁有所需的資源和人員，更好地確保聯合國系統內部的問責制。<br />\n<br />\n麥考爾說：「我們擁有適量的美國接觸和領導力，對那些試圖破壞聯合國創建理念的人實施反制，以便我們能夠以最佳的方式共同解決國際問題。這點很重要。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/08/08/942253.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.secretchina.com%2Fnews%2Fb5%2F2020%2F08%2F08%2F942253.html&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW1Fonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=b728fdf1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.secretchina.com/news/b5/2020/08/08/942253.html</a>"},{"pid":"123efc113b5188ec8394a53d6838853fa40be5e8","tid":2146195,"uid":2889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"岩呀 支持"},{"pid":"1810a63e7c3ba8184a1ed4144141b57d1b1e0a4d","tid":2146195,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:33:55.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0551d2bc5fd23d22060f45c345c02d32c33d7e7d","tid":2146195,"uid":21493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"議案要求擴大目前有關美國向聯合國交納會費的報告程序，要求報告在向國會提交後的14天內在網上公布，使公眾能夠看到。"},{"pid":"bc13240a2b98f79a0ae376289cc320fe1e392754","tid":2146195,"uid":127575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:36:59.000Z","msg":"民主黨一定反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c4e9cacc85a34c1dbc7a679b352968396245bf2","tid":2146195,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8505b529519061010ef394bc48a6a33792d328","tid":2146195,"uid":249979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:45:40.000Z","msg":"一早要清算聯合國啦<br />\n如果通過唔到呢個議案, 應該要成立一個新聯合國去取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68b3fd80979102089b7cb8e0bb82b4707fc80c5d","tid":2146195,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"123efc113b5188ec8394a53d6838853fa40be5e8","tid":2146195,"uid":2889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T12:28:21.000Z","msg":"岩呀 支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T13:33:42.000Z","msg":"樓主pin 佢twitter ac<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepMcCaul\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepMcCaul&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW1Fonr%2Ff8v5Znl2OhmZ9BMM%3D&h=b6e57d2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepMcCaul</a>"},{"pid":"115d43c2c98d89eaf4ddcd5d5a13e81a18136634","tid":2146195,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0